Package: ndstools
Type: Package
Title: Nonlinear Dynamical Systems Data Analysis Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Barney Ricca
Maintainer: Barney Ricca <barneyricca@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides a number of routines for nonlinear dynamical systems (NDS) data analysis. Where possible, these routines include sensible defaults and are intended to run quickly and to be useable by those with only cursory backgrounds in NDS.
    Many other packages exist that implement NDS data analysis routines; where appropriate packages exist, the README file in the repository has notes about many of the other packages; those functions are not reproduced here.
License: MIT License
Encoding: UTF-8
